  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWe currently have a database schema downgrade for the Capella schema (v14). Due to the recent addition of the `HistoricSummaries` column in the freezer database it will be unsafe to apply this schema downgrade once Capella has occurred. As such we should adjust the `downgrade_from_v14` logic to error if Capella has already arrived.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/26787412cd5e5447f00123b4e4afe5d779765b0f/beacon_node/beacon_chain/src/schema_change/migration_schema_v14.rs#L40-L43",
